PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?dog ?dogLabel ( ( ( ( YEAR( ?dod ) - YEAR( ?dob ) ) * 365 ) + ( ( MONTH( ?dod ) - MONTH( ?dob ) ) * 30 ) + ( DAY( ?dod ) - DAY( ?dob ) ) ) / 365.25 AS ?lifespan ) WHERE {
  ?dog wdt:P31 wd:Q144 .
  ?dog wdt:P569 ?dob .
  ?dog wdt:P570 ?dod .
  ?dog rdfs:label ?dogLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?dogLabel ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?lifespan )
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1
